{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"4294967294","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/famoso/layout,_N_T_/famoso/page,_N_T_/famoso"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"es\" class=\"dark\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"/logos-bonchona/92.png\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/b03025bd27638f5f.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-b9cb49113c311c46.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-d86aaf8bdbc2a12a.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/517-8c281142d0b1ae72.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-0f5f228f9d281230.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/173-a967cceac8487976.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/page-8abebbe0e0516216.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/layout-4c0a33c99f3d8f66.js\" async=\"\"></script><title>Radio Bonchona | La que te gusta</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"La radio más popular. Escucha en vivo, entérate de las noticias y vuélvete famoso.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/logos-bonchona/ico.png\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"__variable_246ccd __variable_4c40f6 antialiased bg-background text-foreground pb-24\"><nav class=\"fixed top-0 w-full z-40 bg-background/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-white/5\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity\" href=\"/\"><img src=\"/logos-bonchona/92.png\" alt=\"Bonchona\" class=\"h-10 object-contain\"/></a><div class=\"flex gap-6 text-sm font-medium\"><a class=\"hover:text-brand transition-colors\" href=\"/famoso\">Publicidad &amp; Talento</a></div></div></nav><main class=\"pt-16 min-h-screen\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center w-full min-h-screen\"><section class=\"w-full py-24 px-6 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><h1 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-6 italic uppercase\">IMPULSA TU <span class=\"text-brand\">MARCA.</span></h1><p class=\"text-zinc-400 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto\">La vitrina comercial más potente del centro del país. Planes diseñados para empresas que buscan resultados reales y presencia de impacto.</p><div class=\"mt-8 inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-brand/10 border border-brand/20 rounded-full\"><p class=\"text-brand text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase\">🎵 Atención Artistas: Los músicos no pagan por sonar. <span class=\"underline cursor-pointer ml-2\">Envía tu demo aquí.</span></p></div></section><section class=\"w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-zinc-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 rounded-3xl p-10 flex flex-col hover:border-brand/30 transition-all group\"><div class=\"mb-8\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-black mb-2 italic uppercase group-hover:text-brand transition-colors text-white\">Presencia <br/>En Vivo</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-500 text-sm\">Ideal para marcas que quieren asociarse a nuestros locutores estrella.</p></div><div class=\"text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-white\">$200<span class=\"text-sm text-zinc-600 font-bold tracking-widest ml-2 uppercase\">/mes</span></div><ul class=\"space-y-4 mb-10 text-sm text-zinc-400 flex-grow\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 font-medium\"><span class=\"text-brand\">●</span> Menciones en programas en vivo</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 font-medium\"><span class=\"text-brand\">●</span> Presencia en el Prime Time</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 font-medium\"><span class=\"text-brand\">●</span> Branding en nuestras redes</li></ul><button class=\"w-full py-4 bg-white text-black font-black rounded-xl hover:bg-brand hover:text-white transition-all uppercase tracking-tighter text-sm\">Contratar Ahora</button></div><div class=\"bg-zinc-900 border-2 border-brand rounded-3xl p-10 flex flex-col relative transform md:-translate-y-6 shadow-[0_30px_60px_rgba(255,79,0,0.15)]\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-brand text-white px-6 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black tracking-[0.2em] uppercase shadow-lg\">Más Recomendado</div><div class=\"mb-8\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-black mb-2 italic uppercase text-white\">Impacto <br/>Mix 3</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 text-sm\">El balance perfecto entre radio en vivo y recordación de marca.</p></div><div class=\"text-5xl font-black mb-8 text-white\">$450<span class=\"text-sm text-zinc-300 font-bold tracking-widest ml-2 uppercase\">/mes</span></div><ul class=\"space-y-4 mb-10 text-sm text-zinc-200 flex-grow\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 font-bold\"><span class=\"text-white\">✔</span> Todo lo del Plan En Vivo</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 font-bold\"><span class=\"text-white\">✔</span> 3 Cuñas diarias (1 minuto c/u)</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 font-bold\"><span class=\"text-white\">✔</span> Rotación en horarios rotativos</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 font-bold\"><span class=\"text-white\">✔</span> Reporte de sintonía mensual</li></ul><button class=\"w-full py-5 bg-brand text-white font-black rounded-xl hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all uppercase tracking-tighter text-sm shadow-[0_10px_20px_rgba(255,79,0,0.3)]\">Dominar el Dial</button></div><div class=\"bg-zinc-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 rounded-3xl p-10 flex flex-col hover:border-brand/30 transition-all group\"><div class=\"mb-8\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-black mb-2 italic uppercase group-hover:text-brand transition-colors text-white\">Sintonía <br/>Total 10</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-500 text-sm\">Dominación total del mercado con máxima frecuencia diaria.</p></div><div class=\"text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-white\">$850<span class=\"text-sm text-zinc-600 font-bold tracking-widest ml-2 uppercase\">/mes</span></div><ul class=\"space-y-4 mb-10 text-sm text-zinc-400 flex-grow\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 font-medium\"><span class=\"text-brand\">●</span> Todo lo del Plan Mix 3</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 font-medium\"><span class=\"text-brand\">●</span> 10 Cuñas diarias (1 a 2 min)</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 font-medium\"><span class=\"text-brand\">●</span> Entrevista especial de marca</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 font-medium\"><span class=\"text-brand\">●</span> Prioridad en eventos externos</li></ul><button class=\"w-full py-4 bg-white text-black font-black rounded-xl hover:bg-brand hover:text-white transition-all uppercase tracking-tighter text-sm\">Plan Corporativo</button></div></div></section><section class=\"w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 border-t border-white/5\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center\"><div><span class=\"text-brand font-black text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 block\">Producción de Audio</span><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8 tracking-tighter uppercase italic text-white\">¿No tienes <span class=\"text-brand\">spot?</span> <br/>Nosotros lo creamos.</h2><p class=\"text-zinc-500 mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed\">Contamos con tecnología de punta y locutores profesionales para que tu marca suene increíble. Elige el método que mejor se adapte a tu presupuesto.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-6\"><div class=\"p-8 bg-zinc-900/40 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl group hover:border-brand/50 transition-all\"><h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-white italic uppercase\">Producción con IA <span class=\"text-brand text-xs ml-2\">Quick &amp; Low Cost</span></h4><p class=\"text-zinc-500 text-sm\">Voces hiper-realistas generadas con inteligencia artificial. Rápido, efectivo y económico.</p></div><div class=\"p-8 bg-zinc-900/40 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl group hover:border-brand/50 transition-all\"><h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-white italic uppercase\">Producción Artesanal <span class=\"text-brand text-xs ml-2\">Premium Outsourcing</span></h4><p class=\"text-zinc-500 text-sm\">Locutores de carne y hueso, edición musical a medida y guionistas creativos dedicados a tu marca.</p></div><p class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-600 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest\">* La producción de spots es un servicio adicional que se suma al costo del plan elegido.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 mb-24 flex justify-center\"><div class=\"w-full md:w-[728px] h-[90px] bg-zinc-900/20 border border-white/5 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative group cursor-pointer\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-brand/5 group-hover:bg-brand/10 transition-colors\"></div><span class=\"text-zinc-700 text-[10px] tracking-[0.5em] font-black uppercase z-10\">Espacio Disponible para Publicidad</span></div></section></div></main><div class=\"fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t border-white/10 z-50 flex items-center justify-between px-6 md:px-12 backdrop-blur-xl bg-opacity-95\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 w-1/3\"><div class=\"relative w-14 h-14 bg-zinc-900 rounded-xl overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center border border-white/5\"><img src=\"/logos-bonchona/92.png\" alt=\"Bonchona Logo\" class=\"w-10 h-10 object-contain\"/></div><div class=\"hidden sm:block\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold text-sm tracking-tight\">Radio Bonchona 107.1</h3><p class=\"text-brand text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] animate-pulse\">Sintonía Total</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-1/3 gap-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\"><canvas width=\"80\" height=\"30\" class=\"hidden md:block opacity-50\"></can